---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Us - DropX" 
    description="Learn more about DropX, the revolutionary peer-to-peer file sharing platform. Our mission is to provide the fastest, most secure, and private way to transfer files online."
>
    <div class="container py-24 md:py-32">
        <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto prose dark:prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-display-md md:text-display-xl mb-8 text-ink">About DropX</h1>
            
            <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-8">
                DropX was born out of a simple idea: <strong>file sharing</strong> shouldn't require giving up your privacy to a cloud provider. 
            </p>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    Our mission is to empower individuals and businesses with a <strong>file sharing platform</strong> that is fast, secure, and entirely decentralized. We believe that your data should travel directly from you to its destination, without ever being stored, scanned, or sold by third parties.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">The DropX Difference</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    Traditional <strong>online file transfer</strong> services act as middlemen. You upload to them, and your recipient downloads from them. DropX removes the middleman by using <strong>peer to peer file sharing</strong> technology.
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
                    <div class="p-6 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-md">
                        <h3 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink mb-2">Absolute Privacy</h3>
                        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Since we never store your files, we can't see them. Your data is end-to-end encrypted and truly private.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-md">
                        <h3 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink mb-2">No Size Limits</h3>
                        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Cloud services limit your <strong>large file transfer</strong> unless you pay. We don't. Send 100GB or more at no cost.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-md">
                        <h3 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink mb-2">Maximum Speed</h3>
                        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Enjoy <strong>fast file transfer</strong> that is only limited by your internet connection speed, not a server's throttle.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-md">
                        <h3 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink mb-2">Universal Access</h3>
                        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">DropX is a <strong>browser-based file sharing</strong> tool. No apps to install, no accounts to create. Just open and share.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">Our Technology</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    DropX leverages WebRTC (Web Real-Time Communication) to facilitate <strong>instant file sharing</strong> between browsers. This allows for <strong>secure data transfer</strong> that is both efficient and highly resilient.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">Join the Revolution</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    Whether you are a photographer sending RAW files, a developer sharing code, or a business professional handling sensitive documents, DropX is the <strong>secure file sharing</strong> solution built for the modern web.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
                    <a href="/" class="px-xl h-[48px] rounded-pill bg-primary text-on-primary font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity flex items-center justify-center">
                        Start Sharing Now
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
